  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1. Multi-Use Cards: Eat, Attack, Move</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120880/extras/32d4872f1a53e46e23bb1367f091823d.avif?t=1741323602\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120880/extras_big/32d4872f1a53e46e23bb1367f091823d.avif?t=1741323602 width=800 height=414 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag a food card on an enemy to attack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag on yourself to eat and gain Block.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag on an empty field to move there.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move towards the target to trigger a special forward throw.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2. Unique Design</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple to read:</strong> Over 80% of cards have only 2 lines of text.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple to synergize:</strong> Most synergies can be performed with just 2 cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Highly Strategic:</strong> Do you optimize for attack, defense, positional, or card advantage?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Highly Replayable:</strong> Enemies and shop cards are all procedurally generated.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Dice Roll:</strong> Each action is meaningful and luck-independent.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Farming:</strong> Every card is in the pool and can theoretically appear in the shop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Number Goes Up:</strong> Can your deck outgrow enemies in the late game?</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1. Multi-Use Cards: Eat, Attack, Move</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120880/extras/32d4872f1a53e46e23bb1367f091823d.avif?t=1741323602\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120880/extras_big/32d4872f1a53e46e23bb1367f091823d.avif?t=1741323602 width=800 height=414 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag a food card on an enemy to attack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag on yourself to eat and gain Block.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag on an empty field to move there.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move towards the target to trigger a special forward throw.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2. Unique Design</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple to read:</strong> Over 80% of cards have only 2 lines of text.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple to synergize:</strong> Most synergies can be performed with just 2 cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Highly Strategic:</strong> Do you optimize for attack, defense, positional, or card advantage?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Highly Replayable:</strong> Enemies and shop cards are all procedurally generated.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Dice Roll:</strong> Each action is meaningful and luck-independent.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Farming:</strong> Every card is in the pool and can theoretically appear in the shop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Number Goes Up:</strong> Can your deck outgrow enemies in the late game?</p></li></ul>",
